@Node SP999 "Space -- 1999 > Force Of Life [#9]"

 @{b}Force Of Life [#9]@{ub} (1974)
 
 A ball of blue light approaches Alpha and while the personnel are suspended in
 time, the light invades the body of technician Anton Zoref. Everything
 apparently returns to normal but massive energy losses are recorded and Koenig
 begins to suspect that Zoref may be the cause.
 
 Possessed with a consuming need for heat, Zoref draws it from any source,
 human or otherwise, as he rampages through the base leaving a trail of dead
 bodies and useless equipment in his wake. Koenig orders power supplies to be
 cut in an attempt to deprive Zoref of light and warmth, but Zoref heads for
 the nuclear generating area.
 
