@Node SP9916 "Space -- 1999 > End Of Eternity [#16]"

 @{b}End Of Eternity [#16]@{ub} (1974)
 
 Investigating a passing asteroid which appears to have an internal atmosphere,
 the Alphans blast their way into a living chamber inside. The explosion
 critically injures the only occupant who is returned to Alpha even though
 Helena feels that he cannot be saved. However, the alien makes a miraculous
 recovery and introduces himself as Balor, a Progron scientist who has achieved
 immortality. Unfortunately, Balor is also a dangerous psychopath who lives for
 the pleasure of inflicting fear and pain.
 
 He requests that Koenig allow him free reign to terrorise the Alphans,
 promising to use his powers of regeneration to keep them alive indefinately
 for his eternal amusement, but Koenig refuses so Balor embarks on a rampage
 of death and destruction.
 
