@Node SP9917 "Space -- 1999 > War Games [#17]"

 @{b}War Games [#17]@{ub} (1974)
 
 Alpha is approached by a fleet of Mark 9 Hawk Warships and, believing them to
 be about to attack the base, Koenig orders the Eagles to open fire. Suddenly,
 the Alphans are fighting a war against alien forces that devastate the base
 leaving it uninhabitable. With 128 dead, Koenig's only hope for his people is
 to seek peaceful co-existence with the enemy, so he and Helena journey to
 their planet to plead their case.
 
 They meet two remote aliens who refuse their request on the grounds that the
 Alphans carry contaminants which would destroy a civilisation that has lasted
 for billions of years. Helena is held captive by the aliens while Koenig
 returns to Alpha to prepare for an invasion.
 
